  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave it to me, the money what I gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to go from place to place, to all the best Ukrainian-- to all [INAUDIBLE] what has [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody will even-- they won't listen to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till I came at the one place, Ukrainian, the name is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had five boys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was known to all five boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was called [NON-ENGLISH], did for himself-- went looking for Jewish people to kill, to kill them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, I was with them goy, very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I saw-- and I told them the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I say, [NON-ENGLISH], I am [NON-ENGLISH] now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You want-- you want, you can hiding me and my wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I said, you know, I pay you so much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You won't have to work, and your family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you want, of course if you want, you can kill me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody will kill me, we wouldn't have nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, one thing I can tell you, mine all four brothers, they are near here, hiding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I put on by rich people, now, should even taking on too-- too-- I-- on-- other people do and he go doing that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, Ian, I told him, I'm going to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why I told him this, should-- it was-- it was not true.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, should he think and know yet, I don't-- you not killing me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he say oh-- and he say, I'm going to tell my-- my wife, ask-- ask what she say.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He went to his wife in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was over there, keep talking, talking, till about 20 minutes after he came out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He say, you know, [NON-ENGLISH], my wife told me, she say, a good Jew like you, we must save.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
